Pensacola, its executive officer (who has Nashville ties), a monument to a man who aided the fight for Polish freedom (whose descendants have Nashville ties), antique furniture from Lebanon, Tennessee, and three ads, one of which features a local child. 16 x 21.5 in. Forms part of the Nashville Newspaper Rotogravure Digital Images Collection.
